<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine - Model Years Late 1997 to 2003 - Turbocharger - Assembly (Standard
        Torque Only)
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Assembly (Standard Torque Only)</title>
        <svcproc graphiccount="1">
            <title>Install Turbocharger Pedestal</title>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Late 1997 Model Year, the turbocharger and pedestal are removed from the crankcase as an
                        assembly. 1998 Model Years and up, the pedestal and turbocharger are removed separately.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <figure>
                <graphic filename="../figeg2/eg2500.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="392px" box="yes"/>
                <caption>Attaching the Turbocharger to the Pedestal (Late 1997 Model Year Shown)</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Turbocharger Pedestal</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Pedestal Mounting Bolts</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Turbocharger</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">If removed, install the solenoid valve and tighten the mounting bolt.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Lubricate and install new oil supply and oil drain O-rings onto the pedestal.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Apply Never-Seez&#8482; to the threads of the four mounting bolts. Install and tighten
                    the mounting bolts to the special torque value.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
